                    </div>
                    <span>When I first read it years ago, and rereading it today, I find a lot in this book that is insightful and, moreso, true. The author gives a look into the trends, ways, and lives of the N-Gen that is intriguing. Being one of this generation, it is like looking into my past and recalling my childhood.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Best of the best.</div>
